snippet.title: @canonindiapvtltd  Deleted My FILES !!?? | Only Girnar Survived‚Ä¶üì∏ | Not Blaming‚Ä¶ But‚Ä¶
snippet.description:
Canon, I am NOT blaming you ‚Äî but that‚Äôs what happened.
For the record: I was KIDDING about compensation üòÖ
Love you, Canon! ‚ù§Ô∏èüì∏

Our monsoon adventure began with pure excitement ‚Äî the first day was packed with travel to Somnath, wild moments in the National Park, and beautiful rains that made everything cinematic. I captured it all with my Canon camera, thinking these would be memories I‚Äôd relive forever.

But that night, things took a turn I never expected.
While trying to transfer the footage using the official Canon Camera Connect app, the camera refused to connect. After multiple retries, I uninstalled and reinstalled the app. That was the mistake.

The app asked for a few permissions again ‚Äî I tapped Allow, thinking it‚Äôs normal. Seconds later, every single file from Day 1 vanished from the SD card without warning. No confirmation, no undo ‚Äî just gone. üòû

Canon, I am not blaming you but that's what happend!!
I didn‚Äôt delete anything ‚Äî your app did.

So what you‚Äôre watching now is only Day 2 ‚Äî our unforgettable Girnar trek filled with crazy crowd, misty views, and pure chaos. This video is all that‚Äôs left of an otherwise beautiful trip.

üéß Intro Music : DDG Junagadh Outro (feat. Aditya Gadhvi) ‚Äì pure Gujarati energy!
üéß Music used: All tracks are licensed from Epidemic Sound.
üé• Shot on: Canon + Pain.

snippet.title: F1 car in dubai mall !! DUBAI Part-3 || burj khalifa,Dubai Mall,Desert Safari || Swaminarayan temple
snippet.description:
Dubai Adventures Part 3 & 4 | Burj Khalifa, Dubai Mall, Desert Safari, and More!

Join us on the third and fourth days of our Dubai trip as we explore some of the most iconic locations in the city! In this vlog, we start off at the towering Burj Khalifa, followed by a visit to the luxurious Dubai Mall where we catch a glimpse of an incredible F1 car. Our adventure continues with a thrilling desert safari, complete with sand dunes and fruit hukka!

On Day 4, we visit the largest mosque in Dubai and the serene Swaminarayan Temple, taking in the beauty and culture of this magnificent city.

Special thanks to Arctic Monkeys for their incredible track "Do I Wanna Know?" which sets the perfect tone for my intro!

snippet.title: ‚Çπ114,280 fine-Taking Car Photos Without Owner's Consent ! DUBAI-VLOG || Part 1 ||  #dubai  #vlog
snippet.description:
You can take pictures of cars, but if the owner is inside the car, it‚Äôs not appropriate to do so without permission. Either don‚Äôt take the photo or ask for permission first.
I was taking photos of a cars..he saw that i took a photo of his car and honked but I didn‚Äôt think much of it at first and assumed it wasn‚Äôt directed at me. After walking a few steps, I stopped again to take more pictures. That‚Äôs when the owner approached me and informed me about a 5000 dirham fine. He explained that if a car owner complains about someone taking photos of their vehicle without permission, a fine of 5000 dirhams could be imposed.
.
.

snippet.description:
## Manali Misadventures and Magic (Budget Trip!) - 4 Days in the Himalayas 

**Hey everyone!**   Are you looking for an epic adventure in the Himalayas on a budget? Join me on this crazy 5-day trip to Manali, where we encountered some unexpected turns but also some incredible experiences! Ô∏è  This video is all about the good, the bad, and the hilarious of budget travel in Manali.  

**Here's a sneak peek of what you'll see:**

* **Beautiful locations:** Witness the stunning scenery of Manali, Sissu, Kullu, and the majestic Anjani Mahadev.  Ô∏è‚ùÑÔ∏è  We'll also explore the refreshing Jogini Waterfall.  
* **Scooter adventures:** Buckle up as we rent Activas and navigate the scenic roads on a thrilling ride!   
* **Accommodation drama:**  Oh boy!  We'll share our experience with Manali Nest (not recommended!), and how Karan from Hotel Apple Flower saved the day with their awesome rooms at a great price.   (Thanks Karan!   9813824007)
* **Budget tips:**  Learn from our mistakes and triumphs as we navigate sightseeing and travel options on a budget.   

**Special shoutout to Dhyey, my friend, for lending me the camera!  Although those clips from your place mysteriously disappeared... ** (We'll get you next time, Dhyey!)

**Stay tuned for the full video to see the breathtaking landscapes, the hilarious mishaps, and the valuable tips you won't want to miss!**  Don't forget to like and subscribe for more adventures!
